# Signed Codex artifacts are sealed per engine node, with that node's instance
# identity key (~/.concordance/instance_key.json). They are NOT version-controlled
# — each authoritative engine seals its own. Re-seal with:  python -m api.codex seal
# (or POST /codex/seal). Served at /codex/artifact, verified at /codex/verify.
*.json
!.gitignore
